91,"parent_id":49920,"type":1,"commentor":9613,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"我就是。。。你可以跟我聊聊，我基本痊愈了","anonymity":0,"any_name":null,"commentCount":null,"user":{"id":9613,"name":"瓜摊老板","avatar_url":"http://test01-20200725.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/image/1668349958444.jpg?Expires=1983709950&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4G5RL7pjavqASCwc42kR&Signature=ttH6txvLX08GEEu24zipZeSs%2FTo%3D"},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":189795,"parent_id":49920,"type":1,"commentor":10320,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"我可能抑郁2年，双向3年了，都习惯了…别依赖药物，有时候药物只会让你脑子越来越无法思考。多去感受这个世界美好的事情，多出去玩，多睡觉，多和朋友一起。","anonymity":1,"any_name":"四川麻辣烫","commentCount":null,"user":{"id":10320,"name":"U_67541665068","avatar_url":null},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":189873,"parent_id":49920,"type":1,"commentor":10499,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"我也是，五年双向，大概和前面那个拉面说的一样，躁期和郁期完全不是两个人，我的表化是比较快的类型，所以我会在躁期努力去填满自己的生活（为了控制情绪发泄哈，如果太闲的话会疯的，有动力就尽量别闲下来），郁期就好好休息，不要强迫自己，等待下一次交替。  \n我个人认为最好避免太过激烈的情绪波动，例如狂喜和狂怒崩溃","anonymity":0,"any_name":null,"commentCount":null,"user":{"id":10499,"name":"路过的淑女","avatar_url":null},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":189884,"parent_id":49920,"type":1,"commentor":10499,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"然后还有一点，躁期的时候尽量多学多考标化…我是国际生，高三一整年刚好碰上郁期，一整年都在换着理由请假在家，所以我申请大学的成绩都是我高一高二躁期的时候冲出来的，因为不知道郁期会颓废到什么程度，所以最好做好准备","anonymity":0,"any_name":null,"commentCount":null,"user":{"id":10499,"name":"路过的淑女","avatar_url":null},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":189958,"parent_id":49920,"type":1,"commentor":9821,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"唉，说起来双向，虽然严重的要死，现在基本康复并且停药。大学刚开学时，我记得很清楚，那次躁期过后的郁期，我在路上止不住的大哭流眼泪，根本无法停止；后来慢慢的，越来越喜欢身边的环境，室友、朋友、老师等等都和我合拍，给足了我安全感，自己越来越自信，吃药让我的头脑不清醒，好处是我不会那么敏感","anonymity":1,"any_name":"喷火龙","commentCount":null,"user":{"id":9821,"name":"U_616081662455","avatar_url":null},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":189794,"parent_id":189789,"type":2,"commentor":592,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"双向容易把身边人搞崩溃","anonymity":1,"any_name":"Jerry","commentCount":null,"user":{"id":592,"name":"xxl","avatar_url":"http://test01-20200725.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/image/1664352859085.jpg?Expires=1979712854&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4G5RL7pjavqASCwc42kR&Signature=jqrJUes41AT1wXmBa32L8fBdjCs%3D"},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":189796,"parent_id":189791,"type":2,"commentor":592,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"寻找专业医生，不要过多接触不是专业的心理疏导，有即时需要也可以先看看学校心理咨询","anonymity":1,"any_name":"Jerry","commentCount":null,"user":{"id":592,"name":"xxl","avatar_url":"http://test01-20200725.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/image/1664352859085.jpg?Expires=1979712854&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4G5RL7pjavqASCwc42kR&Signature=jqrJUes41AT1wXmBa32L8fBdjCs%3D"},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":189804,"parent_id":189791,"type":2,"commentor":898,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"还是寻找专业医生会好很多，基本痊愈其实也会有后续影响，且不说生活学业，对身边人亲人朋友恋人也是同理","anonymity":1,"any_name":"深海鳕鱼堡","commentCount":null,"user":{"id":898,"name":"枔_YYY","avatar_url":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/PrFG9C2KicTNWasiahXk8fNOsssOkdKTkgIwBYkTdNtuBOLmQcFNEwL1pyapwrH5XyBz8DH22sHiaDRKdGCWoOYsg/132"},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":189807,"parent_id":189791,"type":2,"commentor":10245,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"怎么才算痊愈？","anonymity":1,"any_name":"Kelly","commentCount":null,"user":{"id":10245,"name":"今天暴风雨","avatar_url":null},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":189812,"parent_id":189807,"type":2,"commentor":9613,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"心态改变","anonymity":0,"any_name":null,"commentCount":null,"user":{"id":9613,"name":"瓜摊老板","avatar_url":"http://test01-20200725.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/image/1668349958444.jpg?Expires=1983709950&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4G5RL7pjavqASCwc42kR&Signature=ttH6txvLX08GEEu24zipZeSs%2FTo%3D"},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":189813,"parent_id":189812,"type":2,"commentor":10245,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"不用医院的诊断证明作为参考吗？","anonymity":1,"any_name":"Kelly","commentCount":null,"user":{"id":10245,"name":"今天暴风雨","avatar_url":null},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":189815,"parent_id":189813,"type":2,"commentor":9613,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"我觉得就算有你有时候也会不舒服出现情绪波动","anonymity":0,"any_name":null,"commentCount":null,"user":{"id":9613,"name":"瓜摊老板","avatar_url":"http://test01-20200725.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/image/1668349958444.jpg?Expires=1983709950&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4G5RL7pjavqASCwc42kR&Signature=ttH6txvLX08GEEu24zipZeSs%2FTo%3D"},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":189821,"parent_id":189812,"type":2,"commentor":10892,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"别误导人，心态的改变完全不能作为痊愈的标准","anonymity":1,"any_name":"多喝热水","commentCount":null,"user":{"id":10892,"name":"U_36601667548","avatar_url":null},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":189825,"parent_id":189815,"type":2,"commentor":10245,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"正常情绪不好出现的波动和双向出现的波动完全不一样，不能偷换概念吧，我自我感觉会经常性的亢奋然后再跌入低谷，亢奋的时候自我感觉良好，那个时候也以为自己好了，其实不是，该抑郁的时候还是会彻底迷失","anonymity":1,"any_name":"Kelly","commentCount":null,"user":{"id":10245,"name":"今天暴风雨","avatar_url":null},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":189832,"parent_id":189821,"type":2,"commentor":9613,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"我哪误导人了。。。真无语","anonymity":0,"any_name":null,"commentCount":null,"user":{"id":9613,"name":"瓜摊老板","avatar_url":"http://test01-20200725.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/image/1668349958444.jpg?Expires=1983709950&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4G5RL7pjavqASCwc42kR&Signature=ttH6txvLX08GEEu24zipZeSs%2FTo%3D"},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":189837,"parent_id":189832,"type":2,"commentor":592,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"确实不能单单以心态转变作为痊愈的标准啊，在躁期的时候也会有这种感觉，这样真的容易误导人","anonymity":1,"any_name":"Jerry","commentCount":null,"user":{"id":592,"name":"xxl","avatar_url":"http://test01-20200725.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/image/1664352859085.jpg?Expires=1979712854&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4G5RL7pjavqASCwc42kR&Signature=jqrJUes41AT1wXmBa32L8fBdjCs%3D"},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":189849,"parent_id":189832,"type":2,"commentor":10892,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"冒犯了，但是单以心态转变来认为痊愈真的很草率，我一个双向的我觉得有点荒谬","anonymity":1,"any_name":"多喝热水","commentCount":null,"user":{"id":10892,"name":"U_36601667548","avatar_url":null},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":189874,"parent_id":189873,"type":2,"commentor":10499,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"狂喜和狂怒啥的，那种兴奋感过了之后会很痛苦，我也说不清是什么，反正就是尽量避免。\n我也没有吃药了，之前医生开了德巴金和一些治疗精神分裂的药（我也不知道为啥会开精神分裂的药），除了让我整个人浑浑噩噩控制不住情绪外没有任何用，我觉得比起看医生，你不如去学校的舒心坊找一下心理咨询师","anonymity":0,"any_name":null,"commentCount":null,"user":{"id":10499,"name":"路过的淑女","avatar_url":null},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":189961,"parent_id":189958,"type":2,"commentor":9821,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"我的睡眠时间长到离谱，9点就开始困，每次睡觉好像陷入了一场昏迷。心态的转变，我慢慢调药停药了。现在是11月，大概大学开学9月中旬停的药，中途明显的就复发过1次…我觉得环境很重要，高中一年多的时间，在校园暴力的持续攻击下度过，一直没有解决，遭受忍受着。所以说建议你找到让自己精神稳定的环境","anonymity":1,"any_name":"三鲜水饺","commentCount":null,"user":{"id":9821,"name":"U_616081662455","avatar_url":null},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":189962,"parent_id":189961,"type":2,"commentor":9821,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"还有就是自救吧，慢慢的我接纳双向，才开始我讨厌不理解，后来我与它共存，郁期会有旺盛的写作灵感，我拿起笔舒展情绪，躁期各方面能力很强，我尽力的享受那刻的开心（不知道我这个观念对不对）。虽说这么久就复发了1次吧，但双向依然存在，只是我慢慢的看开了","anonymity":1,"any_name":"三鲜水饺","commentCount":null,"user":{"id":9821,"name":"U_616081662455","avatar_url":null},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":189963,"parent_id":189962,"type":2,"commentor":9821,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"这就是我的经历吧，希望楼主能看见，有什么想法可以进一步交流一下，祝你顺利","anonymity":1,"any_name":"三鲜水饺","commentCount":null,"user":{"id":9821,"name":"U_616081662455","avatar_url":null},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0},{"id":190181,"parent_id":189958,"type":2,"commentor":1369,"gmtCreate":null,"gmtModified":null,"like_count":0,"content":"谢谢，看到啦。不过很想问医生不让停药，为什么大家都停药了","anonymity":1,"any_name":"Jerry","commentCount":null,"user":{"id":1369,"name":"藜末","avatar_url":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/DYAIOgq83eplq2qibg54eDDxKOY5DclaRw1ze1v2m07hWtUuXUM44GibUqOebJ5EP9zIvwI3hIoeL2V9nVKNtibrQ/132"},"isCommentLike":-5,"dislike_count":0}],"any_name":"Jerry","relation":-2,"liked":-4,"anonymity":1,"dislike_count":0}